data.title: Joseph Joseph - Citrus Catcher
data.description: Keep the pips out of your juicing efforts with this clever little adaptation of a classic reamer. The secret? A special cup catching debris while the liquid runs merrily through. Ext-ream-ly handy!

data.title: Joseph Joseph - Multi-peel
data.description: Ergonomic easy-grip handle and in-built scraper for muddy veg, this multi-faceted multi-peel even has a handy potato eye remover. Now that's a-peel-ing!

data.title: Joseph Joseph - Nest Measure
data.description: Compact measuring spoon set ranging from little (¼ tsp) to large (up to 250 ml). Snap-together for space-saving storage!

data.title: Joseph Joseph  - Easy-Press Garlic Crusher
data.description: We’ve got a new crush. This 2-piece garlic crusher comes complete with a handy in-built scraping tool - you don’t even need to peel! It washes easily too, thanks to special cone­-shaped holes.

data.title: Joseph Joseph - Twist Grater, Coarse and Fine
data.description: Ever find preparing carrots or cheese a little...grating? This microplane changes everything. Two sets of stainless steel, razor sharps blades promise a swift and easy grate every time!

data.title: Joseph Joseph - Elevate Steel Tongs
data.description: These super tongs put hygiene first - an innovative weighted handle with integrated tool rest keeps mess at bay. Gently spring-loaded and comfortable to hold, they're heat resistant up to a smoking 270ºC.

data.title: Bramley Hand Wash and Hand Cream Set
data.description: Bramley uses 100% natural ingredients, just like us. This beautiful set includes full-size bottles of revitalising lavender, orange and geranium hand wash and nourishing aloe vera, grapefruit and cocoa butter hand cream. Sumptuous scrubbing!

data.title: Salthouse & Peppermongers Specialist Mill Set
data.description: Diamond-sharp ceramic mechanism. Classic, sleek design. Adjustable grind. This is the Rolls-Royce of mill technology, complete with a lifetime guarantee. Season with style this Christmas!

data.title: Serious Pig Snackingham Classic
data.description: It's not a village in Hampshire, it's a snack revelation! Finest British pork is infused with caraway, fennel, coriander and black pepper, cured and air-dried before being sliced into a seriously tasty, bite-sized snack. High in protein and low in fat.

data.title: Mr. Filbert's French Rosemary Almonds
data.description: Bittersweet, fragrant rosemary with Mr Filbert's air-roasted, hand-tossed almonds - simple delicate, award-winning flavour. Crush over salads for extra punch and crunch!

data.title: Mr. Filbert's Moroccan Spiced Almonds
data.description: Mr Filbert’s snacks are hot-air roasted and hand-tumbled in 100% natural ingredients. This versatile almond, chilli, mint, cumin and garlic flavour is brilliant crushed over crumble or curry!

data.title: Chocolarder Caramelised Nibbed Cacao
data.description: Unmistakeable ‘raw’ tastes and textures from nibbed Peruvian cacao beans, caramelised and folded through single origin dark chocolate - a whiskey flavour with crunch.

data.title: Chocolarder Peruvian Dark
data.description: Decadent and bold, this single origin bar of lusciousness is infused with the caramel and earthy tones of rare, sustainably farmed Criollo beans.

data.title: Chocolate Mug Brownie
data.description: Just add butter and water, pop in the microwave and behold! A velvety Belgian chocolate brownie miracle in a mug.

data.title: Sticky Toffee Pudding Mug Kit
data.description: Rich toffee sponge drenched in decadent, Madagascan vanilla sauce. A luxurious dessert to fall head over heels for. Four irresistible helpings, ready in just 10 mins

data.title: Iced Cinnamon Bun Baking Kit
data.description: Just add butter and milk for 12 luxury buns of silky cinnamon bliss. Swirls of pure heaven, created by Michel Roux OBE; a sweet classic for you to bake from scratch.

data.title: Extra Virgin Spanish Olive Oil
data.description: The good stuff. This fruity, intense and unique Spanish virgin oil is made the same way it has been for centuries, without the use of any fertilisers or pesticides, from hand-gathered olives at the perfect point of ripening. You won’t see this oil in your local supermarket!

data.title: Peppermongers Black Pepper
data.description: Organically grown, hand-harvested and sun-dried in the hills of the Western Ghats, India, Tellicherry is the highest quality black pepper in the world. Only the fruitiest, largest 10% of peppercorns make the grade!

data.title: Cocowel Coconut Oil
data.description: 100% natural coconut oil, cold pressed for great flavour. A super-healthy alternative to butter. Unrefined, unbleached and unbelievably good!

data.title: Pots & Co - Little Pot of Chocolate
data.description: The perfect midweek gluten free treat! This little pot of luxurious chocolate ganache is crafted with the finest 70% Belgian chocolate.

data.title: Pots & Co - Little Pot of Salted Caramel
data.description: When you add a touch of salt to caramel, something delicious and slightly dangerous happens. We’re championing that danger in the name of these gluten free pots of pure chocolate with salted caramel JOY.

data.title: Pavillion des Trois Arches Merlot
data.description:
This juicy, full-bodied Merlot is made with grapes from Languedoc region of France. It’s Vin de Pays d’Oc classification allows experimentation, resulting in a style that is smooth, rich and modern. It’s a sumptuous partner to red meats, such as our Spiced Lamb Burger.
ABV 13%

data.title: Big Bombora Shiraz
data.description:
A ‘bombora’ is a large sea wave breaking over a reef. True to its name, this South Eastern Australian Shiraz is an ocean of juicy cassis flavours with ripples of red berries, spice, brambles and black pepper. It will go perfectly with our Spiced Lamb or Double Chipotle Burgers.
ABV 13.5%

data.title: Tavino Sangiovese
data.description:
This smooth red is made in the heart of Italy from grapes picked at their ripest. It’s brimming with the fruity aromas of cherries, plums, raspberries and redcurrants with a rewarding, long finish. At its best with meaty or tomato based dishes such as our Rosemary Lamb Meatballs.
ABV 11%

data.title: San Giorgio Pinot Grigio
data.description:
This vibrant, refreshing Pinot Grigio sets itself apart from the pack, thanks to a commitment from its makers to preserve the aromatic scents which define the grape’s variety. It’s refreshing citrus and floral notes make it a match made in heaven for our Tuscan Fish Risotto!
ABV 12%

data.title: Valle Berta Gavi
data.description:
Made from Cortese grapes harvested on the hills of Alessandria in Northern Italy, this elegant, dry white is at its best with our seafood or pork dishes. Citrus aromas of grapefruit and lime couple with white peach notes for a crisp, clean finish.
ABV 12%

data.title: Magic Rock Rapture Red Hop Ale
data.description: 5 types of malt and 6 types of hops make this beer  a truly elating experience. Uplifting aromas of grapefruit and pine, combine with pithy orange and tropically citrus flavours which are balanced against a deeply rich and malty body. 4.6% ABV

data.title: Mighty Fine Honeycomb Salted Caramel Dips
data.description: It doesn’t get more irresistible than this signature light & crisp honeycomb. Flavoured with sea salt & wrapped in caramel-infused Belgian milk chocolate – it’s a treat which makes a real difference – with money from each pack sold going to the Friends of the Honey Bee campaign.

data.title: Camino Real Blanco Rioja
data.description: This white Rioja goes particularly well with mildly spiced dishes, and will be great with chicken and fish recipes such as our Light Citrus Chicken. Notes of date and banana make it a flavoursome, interesting wine with just the right amount of complexity. ABV 12.5%

data.title: Mighty Fine Dark Chocolate Honeycomb Bar
data.description: Mighty Fine's signature light & crisp honeycomb in a bar format, covered in smooth Belgian dark chocolate. All the honeycomb is handmade using traditional techniques that have been modified to make the very best honeycomb there is!

data.title: Superbake Spirit Lifter Cookies
data.description: Spirit Lifters Cookies are made from ancient grains, flours, raw cacao and raw coconut sugar, and are guaranteed to put a smile on your face! Perfect for afternoon snacks, healthy lunchbox treats for kids or with your morning cuppa! Gluten free and refined-sugar free. Makes 15 cookies.

data.title: Showdown 'Man with the Ax' Cabernet Sauvignon
data.description: Wherever you go in America, Cabernet is king – and for good reason. Juicy, ripe blackcurrant and wild berry on the nose, complemented by sweet vanilla oak. Rich cassis and black cherry fruit on the palate with a long, soft, juicy finish. Full-bodied and deliciously smooth. 13.5% ABV [California]

data.title: Belinda Clark Raspberry Marshmallows
data.description: This Great Taste award-winning, gluten free Raspberry Marshmallows are handmade in small batches using the finest fruit powder for a real burst of berry flavour.

data.title: La Lisse Soie d'Ivoire Chenin Blanc
data.description: This wine is fantastically food friendly. La Lisse Soie d'Ivoire translates as 'soft ivory silk', which gives a clue to the attractive texture of this sensual Chenin Blanc. Hints of caramel and brioche lead lead to a densely fruity peach palate. A clean, lifted finish. 12.5% ABV [France]

data.title: Pudology- Chocolate Pot (GF) (DF)
data.description: The pudding obsessives at Pudology have created this decadent treat. This irresistibly smooth pot of chocolate ganache is made with Madagascan vanilla and, though you might not believe this when you taste it, it's gluten and dairy free.

data.title: BKD Chocolate Dino Mini Baking Kit
data.description: Fuel kids’ imaginations. Make baking with your family easy, tasty & super fun! Chocolate Dino Biscuits Mini Baking Kit comes with everything you will need to create 10-12 of your very own biscuits, they even include a cookie cutter and edible decorations!

data.title: Serious Pig Classic Snacking Salami
data.description: Serious Pig take their snacks...seriously. This classic snacking salami made with British pork has won a Great Taste Award for its delicious seasoned pork flavour that gets straight to the point - seriously good charcuterie.

data.title: Wanderlust 'Marlborough' Sauvignon Blanc
data.description: 'Wanderlust' is the uncontrollable desire to hit the road and venture out to discover amazing things. That's exactly what this represents – a classic, bright and vibrant Marlborough Sauvignon, perfumed with nettle and lime. You'll also notice ripe tropical fruits and a rich minerality. 13% ABV [NZ]

data.title: Yeastie Boys Bigmouth Session IPA
data.description: Bigmouth is an extra pale, unfiltered hoppy session ale with tropical and white wine notes. Made using hops from Nelson, New Zealand, this ale has a tantalising, lively flavour and dry aftertaste making it a truly memorable tipple. 4.4% ABV

data.title: Knock Knock Shiraz
data.description: We love a bit of superstition – to knock on wood is meant to ensure good luck... and you're in luck with this blockbuster Barossa Valley Shiraz. Dense sweet blackberry fruits on the nose, with a lovely, savoury, almost meaty character and hints of black pepper. 14% ABV [Australia]

data.title: Microplane Premium Zester
data.description: This zester is slender, practical and durable. Made of strong stainless steel which suits any kitchen, it is equipped with a protective cover, comfortable soft touch handle and two rubber anti-slip feet. There's no excuse not to be able to add some tang to every recipe.

data.title: Superbake Morning Dreamer Pancakes (GF) (DF)
data.description: Morning Dreamers Pancake mix is made from ancient grains, flours and baobab powder to pack even more goodness into your first meal of the day. The mix is gluten-free, wheat-free, dairy-free and can be used to make waffles. Makes 15 pancakes.

data.title: Serious Pig Chilli & Paprika Snacking Salami
data.description: Using the finest British pork, these scrumptious salami sticks carefully balance the sharp piquancy of chilli and the smokiness of paprika to create a deep, rich flavour which won them a Great Taste Award!

data.title: Nieto Malbec, Mendoza
data.description: This Argentinian Malbec is incredibly juicy, fresh and tasty! Forty-year-old vines yield concentrated blackberry and plum fruit flavours, with a touch of sweet spice. The palate is silky and warming, with more black fruit and cherries. A great wine with a fresh finish. 13.5% ABV [Argentina]

data.title: Pudology- Chocolate Orange Pot (GF) (DF)
data.description: This pot of smooth chocolate orange ganache is made with Brazilian orange oil for a zesty, moreish treat. You might not believe it when you taste it, but it's also dairy and gluten free!

data.title: Organic Seed & Bean Lemon and Poppy Seed White Chocolate
data.description: Seed and Bean, the UK's only chocolate company to receive a 100% ethical pass mark accreditation, are all about nature and creativity. This creamy, dreamy white chocolate taste sensation contains poppy seeds for an earthy crunch and is infused with Italian lemon oil for a subtle citrus twist.

data.title: Cornish Sea Salt 225g
data.description: Whether you’re a sparing sprinkler or a liberal lasher, salt is one thing you’re guaranteed to need at most meals. This delightfully crunchy, hand-harvested pot hales from the clearest ocean waters in Cornwall.

data.title: Domaine de L'Olibet 'Les Pujols' Cinsault Rosé
data.description: A little gem from Saint Georges d’Orques in the south of France. Delicate, sweet spice aromas lead on to a palate of abundant ripe fruit, lifted by a natural zing and finishing with texture and richness. Full of character. 11.5% ABV [France]

data.title: Fontanino Riesling
data.description: Think Riesling's are sweet... think again! A fine, delicate dry white with classic Riesling aromas of lime, petrol (it's a good thing, trust us!), and a touch of lemongrass. Lively citrus and stone fruit characters are balanced by crisp acidity and mineral notes on the finish. 12% ABV [Italy]

data.title: Novas Gran Reserva Viognier (Organic)
data.description: Exotic, lush Viognier from organically and biodynamically grown grapes in cool climate Casablanca. Golden yellow in colour with a sweet and floral nose with notes of apricot, honey, white peach, and a touch of gooseberry. The fresh palate has great volume and a persistent finish. 14.5% ABV [Chile]

data.title: The Rambler Red
data.description:
From vineyard to vineyard, the Rambler roams high and low in search of the best-value wines around. Made predominantly with the Barbera grape from Italy's Piemonte region. This wine is ripe and approachable, with soft brambly fruits, supple tannins and a rounded finish.
13.5% ABV [Italy]

data.title: Versetto Prosecco Spumante Extra Dry
data.description: Celebrate with this appealing and very approachable Prosecco – 'extra dry' for a hint of honeyed ripeness. Fresh and fruity, with aromas of citrus and orchard fruit. The persistent fizz leads to a clean, refreshing finish. 11.5% ABV [Italy]

data.title: El Viejo del Valle Pinot Noir
data.description: El Viejo del Valle (‘The Old Man of the Valley’) is an exciting find from vineyards deep in a glacial valley in Chile. Deliciously bright and textural, with summer fruits of red currant, raspberry and wild strawberries. A touch of oak adds spice and complexity. 13% ABV [Chile]

data.title: The Real Olive Company Tricolore Pitted Olives
data.description: Perfectly pitted Kalamata olives, picked in the sunniest Mediterranean climes. Marinated in garlic, chilli and basil - these are the sell-out stars of any antipasti.

data.title: Foxhole Craft Gin
data.description: Created using the rare by-products from the 2015 Sussex grape vintage. Re-purposed through craft and skill, Foxhole Gin takes 8,760 hours to make; a full grape-growing season, fermentation and six distillations in a hand built copper still. Award winning craft gin at its finest!

data.title: Los Otros Pinot Grigio
data.description: Deliciously different for Chile, but classically pebbly Pinot. Really 'right and proper' stone fruit characters on the nose and palate. Much more flavoursome than other PGs you'll find out there – it's delicious, with ripe apple and pear flavours, and a crisp juicy finish. 14% ABV [Chile]

data.title: Ontañón Rioja Crianza
data.description: An approachable and modern Rioja. Primarily this is a Tempranillo – however a little Garnacha (10%) is blended into the Crianza to add aroma and body. Bright ripe aromas of black fruit, with hints of liquorice and mocha. Cherry and plum fruit on the palate balance the tannins. 13.5% ABV [Spain]

data.title: Murviedro Fauno Blanco
data.description:
Medal-winning and fantastically fruity blend of 70% Viura and 30% Sauvignon Blanc from sunny Valencia. Fresh peach and citrus aromas lead to a bright, fresh palate. Ripe stone fruit and
gooseberry notes combine with mineral characters to add texture. 11.5% ABV [Spain]

data.title: BKD Raspberry Unicorn Mini Baking Kit
data.description: Fuel kids’ imaginations. Make baking with your family easy, tasty & super fun! Raspberry Unicorn Biscuits Mini Baking Kit comes with everything you will need to create 20-25 of your very own biscuits, they even include a cookie cutter and edible decorations!

data.title: Belinda Clark Belgian Choc Vanilla Marshmallows
data.description: We always think that Vanilla is the benchmark of flavour - if it's good (and these are) then you can deliver something really special. These vanilla marshmallows are covered in a crisp Belgian chocolate shell- amazing on top of a gourmet hot chocolate!

data.title: Moor Beer Company Confidence Red Ale
data.description: Bristol brewers Moor Beer are the brains behind this bold, ruby-coloured ale that's bursting with juicy, fruity hops and rich caramel flavours. It's dedicated to "honouring those who inspire others" – motivational and moreish!

data.title: Domaine Mas Bahourat Merlot
data.description: Smooth, ripe and seriously good. Flavours of prunes, a touch of Earl Grey and bergamot; the tannins are smooth and supple and the finish is fresh. A characterful, good-value red that's dangerously and dependably moreish. 14% ABV [France]

data.title: Leafy Original Kale Crisps
data.description: Lovingly produced, these light yet satisfying kale crisps are air dried to perfection. Delicately seasoned with delicious, natural ingredients, they offer a delicate crunch and come in at under 49 calories a pack.

data.title: Gavi del Comune di Gavi
data.description: Dubbed 'The Chablis of Italy' this fine, single-estate Gavi di Gavi is textured and complex. An enticing nose of white peach and pear, with hints of fresh lime and gooseberry. Fresh and zesty citrus notes and ripe peachy characters, balanced by crisp acidity and mineral notes. 12.5% ABV [Italy]

data.title: Organic Seed & Bean Coconut and Raspberry Dark Chocolate
data.description: Seed and Bean, the UK's only chocolate company to receive a 100% ethical pass mark accreditation, are all about nature and creativity. This bar is infused with Philippine coconut oil and contains almost 40 crushed organic raspberries, blended with cocoa from Sao Tome, West Africa. Yum!
